1. *Lori* je ptica koja živi u tropskim predjelima. (Translation: *Lori* is a bird that lives in tropical regions.)
2. Videla sam predivnog *lorija* u zoološkom vrtu. (Translation: I saw a beautiful *lori* at the zoo.)
3. Kada sam došla kući, moj *lori* me je dočekao glasnim cvrkutom. (Translation: When I came home, my *lori* greeted me with a loud chirp.)
4. Dali smo *loriju* svježe voće da jede. (Translation: We gave the *lori* fresh fruit to eat.)
5. *Lori* je vrsta papige koja ima šareno perje. (Translation: *Lori* is a type of parrot that has colorful feathers.)
6. Naš *lori* voli da leti po stanu i da se igra sa svojim igračkama. (Translation: Our *lori* likes to fly around the apartment and play with its toys.)
7. Moj prijatelj ima dva *lorija* u svojoj kući. (Translation: My friend has two *loris* in his house.)
8. *Lorija* možete videti u mnogim zoološkim vrtovima širom sveta. (Translation: *Loris* can be seen in many zoos around the world.)
9. Kada se *lori* uplaši, on može da ugrize. (Translation: When the *lori* gets scared, it can bite.)
10. *Lorijevi* cvrkuti su veoma glasni i prepoznatljivi. (Translation: *Lori's* chirps are very loud and recognizable.)